{"abstract":[{"text":"Predict lunar and solar eclipses with detailed timing information.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/astronomykit\/eclipses"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"AstronomyKit can search for and predict lunar eclipses, global solar eclipses, and local solar eclipse visibility for specific observer locations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Lunar-Eclipses","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Lunar Eclipses"},{"anchor":"Finding-the-Next-Lunar-Eclipse","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Finding the Next Lunar Eclipse"},{"code":["let eclipse = try Eclipse.searchLunar(after: .now)","print(\"\\(eclipse.kind.name) lunar eclipse at \\(eclipse.peak)\")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Eclipse-Types","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Eclipse Types"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Penumbral","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Moon passes through Earth’s outer shadow"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Partial"}]},{"text":": Part of Moon enters Earth’s umbra","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Total","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Entire Moon enters Earth’s umbra"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"code":["switch eclipse.kind {","case .total:","    print(\"Total lunar eclipse!\")","case .partial:","    print(\"Partial lunar eclipse\")","case .penumbral:","    print(\"Penumbral lunar eclipse\")","default:","    break","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Eclipse-Timing","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Eclipse Timing"},{"code":["let eclipse = try Eclipse.searchLunar(after: .now)","","print(\"Peak: \\(eclipse.pea